備註 Remarks
     This course covers the advanced topics on Computer Vision and Medical Image Analysis. The grades of this course depend on the presentations and written reports. It is assumed that the classmates already have enough background on digital image processing and computer vision. Therefore, the course contents focus on the applications and theories of computer vision and medical related visual techniques. If you are not familiar with computer vision and image processing, the course is not recommended for you.




